        "name": "Season 2",
        "overview": "Best-selling mystery novelist Rick Castle’s unique approach to crime solving may have won over Detective Kate Beckett, but after crossing her, Castle is going to have to do his best work to get her back on his side.",
        "air_date": "2009-09-21",
